{"tid":999686,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［今次仆街鳥］Nikon轉型連續虧損，不敵Olympus","createTime":"2019-01-29T01:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:10:04.000Z","uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"275a7e9962ad4a65bfa41f635e73a97fe6242a39","tid":999686,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihn7rMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fihn7rMs.png&h=61d40393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOlympus於2013年調整策略至集中發展醫療儀器業務，令現時醫療儀器佔收入比7成，，達78.4%，約6163億日圓，相反影像事業只佔7.7%。而東施效顰的泥坑，數年前主力擴展HealthCare事業，但據2018-19年財報，相關產業領域不單發展緩慢，而且連年虧損，在2018-19預計之630億日圓收中，出現30億日圓的虧損，可謂一噘不振，令人忍唆不禁。<br />\n<br />\n泥坑在Healthcare業務上的失敗，印證著這不思進取的公司或將步入永無止境的黑暗期。但，泥坑何時有光明過？<br />\n<br />\n據2018-19財報，泥坑利潤主要來自精密儀器，繼在低納米及EUV光刻技術上不敵ASML，泥坑去年轉為發展LED 面板上的光刻技術，於2018-19年度帶來可觀收入。也許，不久將來會看見Nikon的其他產品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sw2rHi1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSw2rHi1.png&h=de5848bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51d8829dd5059f53243e399b06b90e5793488672","tid":999686,"uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">驗眼啦白痴，63億呀</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"20be86164151e15c1b14443edf90d46486e777d4","tid":999686,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"51d8829dd5059f53243e399b06b90e5793488672","tid":999686,"uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">驗眼啦白痴，63億呀</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"Billion=10億<br />\n將Billion當億係匪國人先誤會<br />\n<br />\n另外泥坑有出眼鏡<br />\n不過無出驗腦機"},{"pid":"dd298aef2756f39f14fa3b097a33b6e4bd31b537","tid":999686,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51